<br />
My sig normally gives away what class I play... but incase that didn't show up, cause sometimes it doesn't, I play a Sorc. <br />
As for the things my Sorc can do that a Necro can't well I can... <br />
kill mobs much faster than an equivalent Necro (a main reason i play my class)<br />
nuke from 36m range<br />
AE mez where Necro only can single target mez<br />
solo AE kite literaly infinate numbers of mobs at once with AE snares and AE nukes, where a Necro can fear kite maybe max 3 mobs at once if there good.<br />
make my self/group/targetsgroup compleately immune to any spell damage type for short periods (assuming its not a curse <img src="images/smilies/mad.gif" border="0" alt="" title="Mad" class="inlineimg" /> )<br />
<br />
Thats just off the bat, and mostly solo focused, but like my point, it gets back to the class having a different feel and playstyle. If you were to REALLY ballance solo play, so that everything a necro can do solo, every other class can do solo, then you WILL end up with one class that has every ability in the game... and that's a game I would not pay to play.<br />
<br />
Another point, I never said it is ideal to have half or more arcane casters on any server as Necro's, but what i am saying is don't complain about there abilities, its what makes necro's, well, necro's. Fear is a perfectly fine ability, within limits. (and yes they may need to tighten those limits somewhat, on that i agree)<br />
<br />
If you look at why people like playing Necro's and blame the lack of Psi's on that, then by proxy your saying &quot;Necro's are too cool, make them crapper&quot;. But if you look instead at the lack of an equivalent reason to play the Psi, or Druid, or any other class, then you are by proxy saying, &quot;My class lacks coolness, fix it please&quot;. And of the two aproaches i bet you get a better response, and ultimately better outcome, with the latter.<br />
<br />
As a Sorc I often contribute ideas with my fellow Sorc on how my class could be made more special, complaining about what makes other classes special, is not the best way to make the game better. If anything it just encourages the devs to make the game crappier.<br />
<br />
and finally, to refute one of your assertions... Necro's can NOT solo better than any other arcane caster, period. They can solo CERTAIN CONTENT better than any other arcane caster, which imho is fine assuming thats the intent of the Devs.<br />
<br />
In summary, blame the content not the class.<br />
<br />
Cheers
                  
