                  Nothing should come close to Rogue/Sorcerer at best 90% (hello broken monks).<br />
Its what we were build for, destroying stuff.<br />
<br />
<br />
Most intelligent sorcerers (jades illusive code me &amp; a few more) around lvl30 would have<br />
told you they'd exept to be 2nd DPS in raids, just behind rogues.<br />
<br />
Why ? Because the class was fundamentally unkillable by spells (Immunity from  Wards)<br />
And we all knew there would be a price to pay for that.<br />
<br />
Things have changed a lot, now i get hit by everything, and have 3K hp less than a rogue.<br />
Not to mention that i spend a huge amount of time dispelling GE (on GCD unlike counterspell).<br />
Did i mention i need healing to DPS ? Even if i dont take AE/DoT dmg ? (CV powa).<br />
<br />
My &quot;Vision&quot; is :<br />
-&gt; No AE, No GE = Sorcerer <br />
-&gt; No AE, GE = Sorcerer     <br />
-&gt; AE, No GE = Rogue        <br />
-&gt; AE, GE = Rogue            <br />
<br />
When i talk about AE i mean &quot;real nasty shit&quot; 3K+ AEs which makes using CV dangerous.<br />
Yes i know BM can heal us for free, and many classes have HoT's.<br />
Still getting 2x 700 Feedbacks (w/o critic) should be a self-limiting factor.<br />
<br />
For a &quot;real example&quot; on Chrylakis Rogues would come on top.<br />
Since we have to Dispell GE (4-8 sec per GE)<br />
then have to come in melee for the AE Mez thingy (no distance aggro reduction)<br />
And cant use CV because his &quot;flechette&quot; deals 5K (so no CV thus Taq+ForceB)<br />
<br />
On Vicus, if you can time your CV, to have 9 10 11 12 13 14 land during<br />
the weakness, sorcerer should own rogues really hardcore.<br />
<br />
On Zaraax it will be tied, with maybe a rogue advantage (see endurance &amp; burst).<br />
<br />
On Senator, its not comparable, since we're here to kill the adds.<br />
<br />
On Silius, its obvious our AE's will put us on top (with enough mana regen).<br />
<br />
<br />
Basically depending on the mob/setup the top spot will be shared.<br />
<br />
PS : Melees will always have the 15sec Burst Advantage because of the way endurance works.<br />
This may change with the BurnStance but i doubt that much.
                  
