		<td class="alt2" style="border:1px inset">
			
				<div>Originally Posted by <strong>PsiKoTicK</strong></div>
				<div style="font-style:italic">See, the whole &quot;it's been decided so oh well&quot; mentality is bad.  You have a class lead here (Jades) working with you to improve your class.<br />
<br />
He and I are guildmates, and as much as EVERY class lead wants their class to be the best - we both agree that Sorcs shouldn't out DPS rogues, and vice versa.<br />
<br />
There HAS to be a balancing factor.  Risk vs Reward.  As it stands, Monks should out DPS EVERYONE due to no agro issues.  Rogues are higher because we simply do more damage, and have next to no agro issues.  Sorcs, unfortunately, have agro issues galore.<br />
<br />
My Risk is that I eat every AE.  Jades is telling me you guys do too, which...  seems odd, that is the benefit of being a ranged class.  I think they are trying to avoid the whole &quot;ranged &gt; melee&quot; aspect that EQ had (aka, rangers were better than rogues for a while, due to equipment, ranged, and no agro).<br />
<br />
Honestly, I have NO issue with sorcs being higher DPS than me, if they suffer similar drawbacks.  My drawback is that I am 2m from the mob, MAX 5m, but with hitboxes, and all that - that never happens.  You are 25m away.  Well, I have gift of peace, you don't.  Meh.  Psis should have a comparable caster buff like pallies have for us.  I think you'd pass rogues in DPS if just THAT change happened.<br />
<br />
As I said, I don't agree with the whole &quot;casters &gt; melee&quot; - if that is the case, why bring melee to a raid?  Damage shields then become meaningless.  All that matters is the tank, the healers, and caster DPS.  My debuff doesn't cut out the raw DPS potential of a sorceror with NO risk.<br />
<br />
So, all I am saying, as a raiding rogue, is that equal risk should have equal rewards.  Your risk right now is WAY higher than mine.  Fix that, and nothing else has issues.  I don't think nerfing rogues or monks is the way to go.  Particularly with whatever they change to make melee haste worth something, which is going to boost us even further.  Honestly, I am thinking they take autoattack off the global timer.  If that happens, my DPS will simply skyrocket, but so will the tank's ability to hold agro.  The tank holding agro better helps all of us.  Talisker gave us rogues what we have because we were falling behind the other melee classes.  Now we're going to be second rate to casters, because Avair thinks we're &quot;too good.&quot;  Something's not right here.</div>
			
		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>
</div>]<br />
<br />
To level out rogues and sorcs remove your 4% crit buff the raid gets.<br />
<br />
Bring our aggro management up to yours and then we are equal.  <br />
<br />
Your 4% crit buff taken over the entire raid is bloody huge dps increase unless we ignore that.<br />
<br />
i guess the big question is do you consider this 4% part of your dps??? cause you really should.<br />
<br />
Sorcs do NOTHING to increase dps for other classes. 0 zilch<br />
<br />
Do not forget this fact when you think our dps should not be higher.
                  
		</div>
